    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, an analog masterpiece in superlative condition. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing high-pressure double VANOS and individual throttle bodies for a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with an M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally sound with no subframe fatigue, and the suspension retains factory-spec kinematics. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been maintained to exacting standards, ensuring peak thermal efficiency and torsional rigidity.",
