      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true collector-grade vehicle in showroom condition. The exterior is finished in a flawless factory paint that has been professionally ceramic coated, resulting in a deep, mirror-like reflection free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Every body panel is original with perfect gaps. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery maintains its original matte texture and 'new car' scent, with no signs of bolster wear or aging. All high-gloss trim pieces are scratch-free, and every electronic feature operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. It has been stored in a climate-controlled environment and has never been driven in inclement weather. Included is a complete set of keys, the original window sticker, and a comprehensive binder of service documentation. This is an investment-grade example for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
